graphify-out/

*.json
*.yaml
*.yml
*.toml
*.lock
*.log
*.txt
*.jsonl
*.gdoc
*.gsheet
*.gslides

**/manifest.json
**/*slack*manifest*
**/app-manifest.*

node_modules/
.venv/
__pycache__/
.git/

.obsidian/
_archive/
logs/
